{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_hamoni_set_1", "eventName": "孤獨的舞者", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "孤獨的舞者", "storyInfo": "阿赫茉妮遇到了一個瞭解她的過去的人，對方提出可以讓她擺脫情報人員的身份，而她沒有同意。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_school", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$calm_loop", "key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#6", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見，洛西莉。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛西莉！", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——啊，親愛的麗塔。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是不是很久沒機會說上話了？真可惜呀，我們沒能像以前一樣，被分到同一間宿舍。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "近衛學校的軍事化訓練，真是比我們之前想像的還要繁重，你說是不是？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你那天，趕上入學考試了嗎？", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#3"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳......怎麼突然問這個？我當然趕上了，不然我怎麼會在這裡？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#3"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒事。給，你的《軍事科學概論》。上面的批註和筆記很有用，多謝了。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "考試當天早上我準備還給你，但是沒等到你。我一直有點擔心。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一起去吃晚飯嗎？我們可以順帶聊聊天，你替我選選休息日穿的長裙。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不了，我正要趕去斯蒂芬妮舉辦的舞會呢。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#4"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說那位萊塔尼亞伯爵的女兒？", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#4"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說她的確有一些人脈，商人要尋找門路，音樂家和劇作家要找人引薦，先進入她的交際圈不會有錯。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上次碰到你的時候，你是要去那位集團軍參謀的外孫女主持的宴會，那樣的軍事家族總是需要培養一些親信。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，那應該都跟你的志向沒什麼關係。過去你是不喜歡那些吵鬧的社交活動的。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼說，麗塔。我就不能只是喜歡跳舞嗎？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那等你下次有閒置時間，我們再聊吧。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼板著臉呀。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是到了新環境，我們都需要一點時間來找到自己的節奏，不是嗎？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哼唱）......就像舞步的節奏。可惜，我多麼希望你能陪我一起呀。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......洛西莉，你還記得我們為什麼要努力考入皇家近衛學校嗎？", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然啦，為了成為優秀的軍人。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。不是軍官，不是軍事貴族，是軍人。我不想當一個像父親那樣只知道明哲保身的斯卡曼德羅斯。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你想像我們的老師那樣，做一個能堅定捍衛秩序的軍人。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的意思是......你如果有什麼心事，可以跟我說。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師過世之後，我們還沒有去她的墓前看望過吧。", "name": "麗塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊，真不好意思，我得走了，麗塔。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_mini02_victoria_street_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報紙上是這麼寫的，“倫蒂尼姆及卡茲戴爾經濟文化交流協會”。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道背後是哪位大公爵，找來那麼一大隊薩卡茲雇傭兵，作為自己放在倫蒂尼姆城內的棋子。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可不這麼想。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，別說別說。您要是知道什麼內幕，也千萬別跟我說。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，哪位大公爵最有可能掌控維多利亞，貴族之間對獅王後裔的下落有什麼傳言，有幾座城市可能會爆發動亂......你都不好奇一下嗎？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道這種事，對我有什麼好處呢？我連您是哪位市議員的家庭教師都不願意知道。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，您家庭教師的身份，應該也是過去式了。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是呀，我昨天剛剛結束最後一次課程。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位年幼的公子已經掌握了足夠多的知識，當然也用不上我了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......是您從他們那裡打探到的消息足夠多了吧。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說，多到我的上級決定自己負責這一帶的事務，為他的榮譽牆再增添幾枚勳章？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳......我可不敢隨便議論別人。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，您應該準備一些手段，避免這樣被搶功。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的事情總會發生，有什麼好在意的呢？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，來一份時尚雜誌。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$book_close", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今後不管是哪位來，只要拿著您的這種特製硬幣，就能買到這份雜誌，我沒弄錯吧？", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，牽線搭橋的工作我都已經做好了，你不會犯錯的。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，你什麼都不知情，就算有人找到你，也不能對你做什麼。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你平靜的生活不會被影響，只會得到我們承諾的報酬。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，您是瞭解我的。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了這筆收入，我的孩子能上更好的學校了，他們會成為真正的紳士。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，您花了多長時間，才磨掉自己身上軍人的英氣？我認識的那些軍官，哪怕脫下制服，我也能分辨出來，您卻不一樣。", "name": "報刊亭老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍人？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......雖然我是軍方的人，但我從來沒有說過，我當過軍人呀。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，還有人邀請我赴宴，我該走了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕將來的某一天，鄰近的城市地塊坍塌，或者聖王會西部大堂血流成河，自己也可以置身事外，維持自己一貫的生活......", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "體面優雅的聰明人，我已經看厭了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，讓我看看......我的好線人會給我帶來什麼樣的消息呢？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這封信......", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......信被人調換過？裡面夾了一張便條。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“......我知道你的身份，但我並非維多利亞的敵人。”", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，這句話可證明不了你究竟是有意協助，還是想將我抓住。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都喜歡說，自己是“為了維多利亞”。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年無論是吊死獅王的人，還是堅定捍衛王室的人，可都同樣覺得自己是在捍衛維多利亞呀。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是各位努力的方向一致，也就不需要我這樣刺探情報的人了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，今晚在宴會上，我還要多傳出去一條訊息，弄清楚這位神秘人士究竟有什麼意圖。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_manorgarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177", "name2": "avg_npc_176", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177", "name2": "avg_npc_176", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽說了嗎？市議會的那些老頑固裡總算有兩個鬆口了，願意再造一批蒸汽戰車，同時出台法令，放寬對工廠主的限制。", "name": "好奇的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177", "name2": "avg_npc_176", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我們花在他們身上的金幣至少沒浪費。", "name": "誇誇其談的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越是上年紀的那些傢伙，越是不敢表態。軍隊增添武備是常事，可是他們就害怕被人問：這是誰的軍隊？要去打誰？", "name": "誇誇其談的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從沒了獅王，這些問題就越來越不好回答了。", "name": "誇誇其談的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177", "name2": "avg_npc_176", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那可不是，上個月病死在床上的那位老議員，你還記得嗎？", "name": "好奇的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽她的鄰居說，那天晚上大家都隱約聽見了慘叫聲。誰敢說她實際上是不是病死的呢？", "name": "好奇的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177", "name2": "avg_npc_176", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是老頑固們不肯放開手裡權力的惡果。", "name": "誇誇其談的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，我們去宴會廳裡，請讓我為您拿一杯酒。", "name": "誇誇其談的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陰謀，賄賂，暗殺......沒有什麼新鮮事。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#6"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該可以去那邊的小陽台見見我的好夥伴了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#6"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚上好，阿赫茉妮小姐。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀......", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您現在有空嗎？", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_singleblunt", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不算太有空，如果您言行不夠謹慎的話，我的源石技藝產生的水流會灌進您的氣管，扼住您的喉嚨。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的反應真快。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的氣色不錯，呼吸也沒有變得急促。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您誤會我了。我混入您的情報網留下一張字條，並不是打算威脅您什麼。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，您找我是有什麼事呢？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有位侯爵派我前來，向您傳達善意。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果您想協助我們的工作，至少應該先帶一些有效的情報來，不是嗎？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我想為您提供一個新的去處。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您被迫成為情報人員，為已經腐朽的獅王軍隊效力，這實在是埋沒了您的資質。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您也不應該再為自己數年前做錯的一件小事受折磨，更何況，您當時完全不知情，這不能算是您的過錯。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他們為了隱瞞那樁醜聞，可是給了我不少好處。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是不是知道得太多了？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師，我回來了，信我已經帶到了。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天就是入學考試了，我還想請教您幾個問題，主要是源石技藝測試方面......", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒有人在？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knife", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbreak", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing1", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing2", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師？您還好嗎？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熟悉的撞擊聲，應該是老師用的那種軍刀的聲音......欸，難道是有人來搶劫？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師那樣身經百戰的軍人，處理幾個匪徒應該綽綽有餘。不過，正好我也可以測試一下自己的能力......", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......走私集團已經全部擊倒！進入倉庫檢查！", "name": "陌生的聲音"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師......霍里女士？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡還有殘餘同夥！", "name": "陌生的聲音"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放下武器！舉起手來！", "name": "陌生的聲音"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們是誰？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G2_opera_room", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_248", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全都問清楚了？", "name": "嚴厲的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經問過了，她是霍里的學生，年紀還小，對該集團倒賣軍方物資的事情一無所知。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她確實多次充當中間聯絡人的角色，幫霍里送信，但她並不知道自己轉交的是什麼，也沒有懷疑過自己的老師。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "霍里退伍後在一所貴族私立中學執教，近五年沒有任何違規記錄，很受學生尊敬。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那名學生本人回憶，霍里沒有拉攏任何學生作為自己同夥的跡象，應該不必再對其他學生進行排查了。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經控制她兩天了，雖然只是普通問話，沒有刻意施壓，但根據觀察到的細節來判斷，她是十分誠實的。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_248"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，讓她進來吧，我們執行上面的安排。", "name": "嚴厲的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_248"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經明白事件的前因後果了嗎？", "name": "嚴厲的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師犯了重罪，我在不知情的情況下成了幫兇......大致上應該是這樣。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......請問，老師她最後......？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_248"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她拒絕配合，甚至率人和軍方發生暴力衝突，只有死路一條。", "name": "嚴厲的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍方物資被倒賣的情況，我們已經追蹤了一年多，霍里憑藉自己過去在軍隊的人脈，成了倒賣鏈條中的關鍵人物，這一點不會有錯。", "name": "嚴厲的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你不要對她有太多同情心。", "name": "嚴厲的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......她是個好老師嗎？", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她......", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是個堅定有力的戰鬥者，我很仰慕她展現出的力量。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起禮儀課或是社交話術訓練，似乎我從她那裡學到的東西更有價值。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果她做了這樣的事情，然後以這種方式失敗、倒下......", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......有些出乎我的意料。僅此而已。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#4"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我尊敬的人，也不過如此而已呀。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#4"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於你在這一事件中受到的衝擊，我們表示理解。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請放心，我們不會追究你的所作所為，也不會將你視作她的同夥。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我們希望你作為唯一知情的平民，務必對這一事件的真相保持沉默。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，霍里將和另外兩名參與倒賣的士兵一起，被記錄為此次行動中軍方的協助者。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你記住，他們是“在交戰中英勇地犧牲”。她的死訊傳到校園後，你對你的同學、老師或者其他人，都應該這麼說。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們還會被追授勳章。希望你能理解我們的良苦用心，為你尊敬的人維護身後的名譽，讓她的死亡能體面一些。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我懂得該在什麼事情上沉默。", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很高興我們能達成共識，你會得到一些好處。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好處？", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自述是為準備近衛學校入學考試而來找她。", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想進入皇家近衛學校，對嗎？", "name": "溫和的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "洛西莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我還在乎嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_manorgarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不過恰好是當年軍隊內的知情者之一。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您是為了來與我敘舊，那您真是太客氣了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，那都已經是好幾年前的事情了，連我自己都記不太清了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是您數年來的境遇令我同情，我不忍心看一名前途無量的年輕人得不到她應有的榮譽。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您應該能感覺到，您的人生在那場意外事件之後就已經不再受自己控制。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管進入了近衛學校，但尚未畢業，您就被迫改換身份隱姓埋名，從事情報工作，連真誠的人際關係都難以搭建。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好在，您同時可以說是十分幸運。眼下侯爵似乎對您的能力青睞有加，在我的引薦下，您可以接觸到他，或許能憑努力成為他的親信。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您既可以從情報人員這一身份中解脫，也能夠獲得更高的地位。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這樣說，能否取信於您？", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是呀，也不過是這些東西而已。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您的意思是？", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別放在心上，只是一句自言自語。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒是覺得，我們維持現在這樣，我的法杖能抵著您喉嚨的距離，顯得更親近一些。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說完，阿赫茉妮卻抽回了法杖。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——請您離開吧。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，如果您是擔心自己作為情報人員難以脫身才拒絕，請相信我們有足夠的手段協助您。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來，您認為我一定要恨我的生活與我的命運才行。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您有一種不算少見的錯覺，生活中處處埋藏著陰謀，許多小事件其實都有您這樣的大人物在背後設計，是不是？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為情報人員，您應該見過許多這樣的情況。", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是呀，已經見得有些厭倦了，甚至也做得有些厭倦了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實際上，沒有人脅迫我做情報工作。幾位老師選中了我，我同意了，僅此而已。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道嗎？如果我真的無力掌控自己的生活，那我現在就必須殺了你，免得你給我招來什麼麻煩。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#4"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我很喜歡你。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#4"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，我們應該都是來參加這場宴會的，是不是？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿赫茉妮輕巧地轉身。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$bar_intro", "key": "$bar_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宴會廳裡，樂隊躬身準備開始演奏，通明的燈火透過落地窗，映亮她的輪廓。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#6", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哼唱）", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#6"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她自顧自地抬手，轉了個圈。"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在庭院裡，她獨自一人跳起輕快的舞步。"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......要與誰共舞呢？", "name": "面色和善的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "名叫阿赫茉妮的菲林沒有回答。"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}